{"tid":880691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「巴西特朗普」當選巴西總統     曾批評中國人買起巴西","createTime":"2018-10-29T01:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T09:59:11.000Z","uid":39464,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"823967054f04713b81968fefeab756b30812fb6e","tid":880691,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T01:46:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20181029_20181029-074734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20181029_20181029-074734.jpg&h=cb060849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴西總統大選第二輪投票結束。被稱為「巴西特朗普」的右翼社會自由黨候選人博爾索納羅，取得超過五成半選票當選。博爾索納羅承諾會改革政府財政，削減赤字，下調利率；外交上會靠近先進大國，令巴西在貿易及科技上受惠。現任總統特梅爾表示，已經準備好交接，強調交接過程會非常平靜。<br />\n<br />\n63歲的博爾索納羅，具有軍方背景。他形象廉潔，在貪污問題嚴重的巴西政壇中，深得選民支持。他的多項理念都緊跟美國總統特朗普，並極力主張國企私有化。他對中國極有戒心，多次發表反對中國投資的言論，批評中國人不是在巴西買東西，而是買起巴西。博爾索納羅就任後將面對嚴峻挑戰，包括盡快帶領巴西走出經濟衰退，以及化解日益嚴重的社會矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1038118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1038118&d=1Fqst2YE4s9YKDTYceK5OYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=dc562d12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1038118</a>"},{"pid":"7209814737dc3e9ddc0c4fbf94288b3918c6f5dd","tid":880691,"uid":69213,"like":3,"dislike":36,"score":-33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:01:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b3841ef9bf3756e685effc19db6ceffce51d33f","tid":880691,"uid":138441,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:02:49.000Z","msg":"全球反支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5133ddd59e8ab7fb2ed818b58bed28c635e363c8","tid":880691,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:05:39.000Z","msg":"巴西侵侵"},{"pid":"46971055e659b2ba3b92701bf112c19fcfe42973","tid":880691,"uid":54381,